'''Marcham Prace''' was a [[Lieutenant/Legends|lieutenant]] with [[New Republic Intelligence Service|New Republic Intelligence]], specifically [[Special Threats Division]]. He was sometimes tasked with dealing with handling security threats, such as the attempted theft of the back-up data storage for New Republic Intelligence.

